e-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"ï¼­ï¼³ æ˜Žæœ\";\r\n	mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n.MsoChpDefault\r\n	{mso-style-type:export-only;\r\n	mso-default-props:yes;\r\n	font-family:Cambria;\r\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;\r\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"ï¼­ï¼³ æ˜Žæœ\";\r\n	mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n@page WordSection1\r\n	{size:612.0pt 792.0pt;\r\n	margin:72.0pt 90.0pt 72.0pt 90.0pt;\r\n	mso-header-margin:36.0pt;\r\n	mso-footer-margin:36.0pt;\r\n	mso-paper-source:0;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n-->\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">\"The perfect place to feel human again.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>The peacefulness of this place is\r\nrejuvenating.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Must be the view, the\r\nbreeze, the flowers,<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>your kindness,<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Thanks!\"<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;\r\n</span>Melissa Dailey, Boston Mass.</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">Hillcrest Guest House is one of the oldest and established\r\nguesthouses, operating as a Bed and Breakfast Inn, home away from home, motel,\r\nvacation rental and a small boutique hotel on Cruz Bay, St. John, US Virgin\r\nIslands. Suites small and large apartments are available; some with canopy\r\nbeds. Designed by Architect Howard Lindqvist, Mom\'s cousin.\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">Located on a hill overlooking Cruz Bay, St. John, US Virgin\r\nIslands and located in an established Caribbean residential area, which\r\nprovides you with a spectacular \"Million Dollar View\".<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Hillcrest is conveniently located adjacent\r\non Cactus Hill Run. <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"http://goo.gl/maps/xe51L\">Google Map of Hillcrest location</a> Close to restaurants, stores, Churches, taxis, banks with\r\nATM machines, fishing, boating, hiking, camping, sailing, cultural excursions\r\nand other places of interest.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>The\r\nAtlantic Ocean is on the North and the Caribbean Sea is on the South.\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">Have you been looking for the perfect place for your\r\nhoneymoon, wedding destination or family adventure? Kids ages 12 and under stay\r\nfor free. Why not explore that picturesque U.S. Virgin Islands? Many seek St.\r\nJohn for their getaway and wedding destination. The pristine turquoise water,\r\nwhite sandy beaches, and fiery sunsets topped with warm breezes are all there.</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">If this is where you want to stay, call 340-776-6774,\r\ne-mail- hillcrestguesthouse@yahoo.com or book on line at <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"http://www.bedandbreakfast.com/virgin-islands-saint-john-hillcrestguesthousestjohnusvirginislands.html\">Bed and Breakfast</a> or <a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"http://www.expedia.com/St-Thomas-And-St-John-Hotels-Hillcrest-Guest-House.h1100483.Hotel-Information\">Expedia</a><br></font></p><font size=\"3\"></font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a target=\"\" title=\"\" href=\"http://www.powell-graphics4.com/calendar/2359/calendar.cgi\">See Calendar</a><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">At Hillcrest Guest House in St. John you will be provided\r\nwith everything you want for your first getaway as a family or couple. You will\r\nfind suites that offer complimentary food and beach equipment. The menu\r\nincludes breakfast items, liquor, and snacks so that you can enjoy your stay to\r\nthe fullest.</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">If you feel adventurous and want to explore the wonders of\r\nthe islands waters, you will have access to beach equipment that includes\r\nsnorkel and fins to see all that the pristine shores have to offer.</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"></span><b>Hillcrest Guest\r\nHouse History</b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"><br></span>Hillcrest is one of the\r\noldest romantic and established small hotels, B &amp; B\'s<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>on St. John. The land was bought in the 1940s\r\nand the vacation rental accommodation was started in 1966 by the Hall Family, the\r\noriginator, Ethlyn Hall, my mother.</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">Overlooking pristine Cruz Bay, St. John, also known as Love\r\nCity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Boats, yachts, sunsets and\r\nsunrises can be seen from here. Similar to a bed and breakfast, in that the\r\ncomplimentary menu includes breakfast items, snacks, drinks and liquor.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Complimentary DVD movies are on site.</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><b>Description of\r\nArea</b></font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">You can walk to Cruz Bay; only 4 minutes to downtown, where\r\nthe restaurants, stores, banks with ATM machines, taxis, tennis court, bars and\r\nchurches are located.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>The ocean can be\r\nseen all around from each suite on the top floor<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>(Front, Caribbean Ocean View, Sunset<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>and Tropical<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;\r\n</span>Garden <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>Suites) and Lounge Area. Music\r\nplayed at the beach bar on Sunday afternoon can be heard, if you listen\r\nclosely.</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p><font size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\">The accommodations are secure, a gated entrance for guest\r\nonly.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Neither dogs nor cats are allowed\r\nin or near guest area. I have two dogs on site; Taj Mahal, known as\r\n\"Taj\" and<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>Dora, the explorer.\r\nWe live on the first floor and the rooms with the ocean views are upstairs.</font></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','340-776-6774','hillcrestguesthouse@yahoo.com','http://www.hillcreststjohn.com/','','',18.328964,-64.795544,'2013-07-09 11:26:32',19,3,0,'2016-05-31 09:38:35'),(426,54,'Centerline Road Overlook','<font size=\"3\">Views north to Whistling Cay, Mary Point, Great Thatch, Jost Van Dyke and Sandy Cay.</font><br>','','','https://','','',18.344386,-64.7516,'2013-07-31 13