helf for months, either in our store or at our suppliers.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\">St. John Spice offers quality and a variety of products that\r\nhave made us a tradition for so many visitors.</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><b><br></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><b>Shipping Available</b></font>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\">We can ship your purchases! Postcards and stamps are also\r\navailable, and we can mail them, too!<b><br></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><b><br></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><b>Location &amp; Hours</b></font>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\">St. John Spice &amp; St. John Spice Too</font></p><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\">9am to 9pm<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><b>Easy to find!\r\n\r\n</b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\">Simply take five steps after leaving the passenger ferry\r\ndock, turn right, then go up the brick stairs<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" size=\"3\">From the cruise ship passenger drop-off area, take a RIGHT\r\nand walk through delightful Cruz Bay town to the passenger ferry dock.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</font></p>','340-693-7046','ruth@stjohnspice.com','http://www.stjohnspice.com/','','',18.331067,-64.795131,'2013-11-08 14:56:31',20,1,0,'2015-07-01 21