	margin:72.0pt 90.0pt 72.0pt 90.0pt;\r\n	mso-header-margin:35.4pt;\r\n	mso-footer-margin:35.4pt;\r\n	mso-paper-source:0;}\r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n--></style><font face=\"arial\" size=\"3\">Come visit us in our NEW LOCATION just steps from the main\r\nferry dock in Cruz Bay<br><br>Join us on our daily scuba diving or snorkeling tours and\r\ndiscover why St. John is more fun UNDER the water.<br><br>Low Key Watersports is a PADI five-star IDC facility. Not\r\nscuba certified or looking to advance your dive certification? We can teach you\r\nin no time! We offer a full range of diving courses from Discover Scuba Diving\r\nand Open Water, all the way up through Divemaster and Instructor! Need a\r\nreferral? We accept PADI, NAUI, SSI and Universal referrals. As a certified\r\ndiver, you can enjoy our daily reef dives, or weekly night dives and wreck\r\ntrips! If you prefer to shore dive, we have a full range of scuba equipment\r\navailable for rent; just stop by our shop.<br><br>Be sure to ask about any other water activities you might be\r\ninterested in! Our staff is happy to help you figure out the best trip for your\r\ngroup including boat rentals, kayaking, dinghy rentals, parasailing, day sails,\r\nsnorkel trips, hobie cats, and trips to the Baths and Jost Van Dyke in the\r\nBritish Virgin Islands.<br><br>Need snorkel gear? Whether you are renting for a week or\r\nbuying a top of the line set, stop by our shop and be properly fitted for\r\nsnorkel equipment! Our store also carries a wide range of men and women\'s\r\nswimwear, rashguards, t-shirts, cover-ups, shoes and more.<br><br>Give us a call and let our friendly staff assist you with\r\nyour watersports reservations. We pride ourselves in making your vacation, a\r\nvacation to remember.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</font>','340-693-8999','info@divelowkey.com','http://www.divelowkey.com/','','',18.330264,-64.796481,'2013-12-05 06:39:22',25,2,0,'2015-07-01 21:01:42'),(565,11,'Ocean Runner','\r\n