ff Point. See yourself standing on the\r\nopen terrace with 270 panoramic views of wildlife and ocean coral reef, a\r\nkaleidoscope of color washing over your senses as you step into the infinity\r\nedge swimming pool or climb the stairs to the lookout tower. Imagine this\r\nunbelievable fantasy sunrise to sunset. You can see how we selected the name!<br>The gates open and as you wind around Ditleff Point and\r\napproach the entrance to our \"fabulous\" Kaleidoscope Villa offered\r\nfor vacation rental in 2010. As the first home planned on Ditleff Point, we\r\nhave used careful and painstaking consideration in every decision for a perfect\r\nluxury vacation retreat - from towels to technology. The unsurpassed waterfront\r\nviews are only one feature to entice those who need a relaxing and private\r\nescape. Kaleidoscope Villa contains four king bedrooms each with private bath\r\nand its own terrace. Step from your bedroom retreat onto the terrace, have a\r\nseat and enjoy the overwhelming ocean view in guilty pleasure. When you are\r\nready to emerge from your bedroom sanctuary, you can gradually reawaken with a\r\nrefreshing beverage on the expansive veranda, soak in the spa, swim in the\r\npool, explore the Kaleidoscope Villa shore, or stroll to the sheltered private\r\nDitleff Point beaches. Both sailboat and sea turtle watching are fantasticOur website guest reservation center provides island\r\ninformation, restaurants and dining recommendations, rental car requests and\r\nspecial event information. We want the planning of your vacation to be as\r\nenjoyable as your time on St. John.<br>Your dream vacation on St. John waits in one word:\r\nKaleidoscope.</font><br>','704-363-6246','jack@kaleidoscopeusvi.com','https://www.kaleidoscopeusvi.com','','',18.318122,-64.766903,'2014-07-12 12:47:32',2,1,0,'2016-05-13 15:10:10'),(613,12,'Calabash Cottages','\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n<!--\r\n /* Font Definitions */\r\n@font-face\r\n	{font-f